snippet.title: The Jimi Hendrix Case Full Playthrough / Longplay / Walkthrough (no commentary)
snippet.description:
Full playthrough of The Jimi Hendrix Case, a bizarre free-to-play detective noir point-and-click adventure in which every character is Jimi Hendrix, recorded by Eric, published 31 December 2023.

The Jimi Hendrix Case is longplay No. 1132 of the Ludophiles longplays project:
- https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLFXG3BI19O5rpA9sB1_-K_x5s207hoahb
- https://ludophiles.com/threads/ludophiles-longplays-project.180/

#ludophiles #ludophilia #longplay #playthrough #walkthrough
